Myrmidon finally leaped out of the Predicon base, his feline form lending him a powerful grace and strength. With a sound that is part growl and part purr he stalked forward watching the battle field. 

"It looks like you have this battle well in hand Hydras." Myrmidon's voice transmitted over the radio to him. "I am sure that the three warriors you have on that single enemy should be quite enough."

Myrmidon chuckled as he moved off to one side, looking for prey . . . 

OOC: Who exactly is out here? I am not sure who is available. I think I know of Hydras, Scorpi, Jhiaxius, Megatron and Grimlock??

Preston
(Myrmidon)
